- WorkSession `initiatedBy` StatusCheck (or StatusReport)
- WorkSession `resultedIn` Task (completion/update)
- WorkSessionSave `pauses` WorkSession
- Task `blockedBy` Error / ExternalFactor
- Code `implements` Task
- Build `tests` Code
````

